Pretend to spank me - I'm a pseudo-masochist

ahahahahahahahahahahaha.
i think too much red bull is affecting my brain.

I'm really just using this journal to read fiction since a lot of posts have that flock thing. I adore reading all sorts of fiction, am not at all homophobic, i'd like to believe i'm largely normal and i especially love vampire/fantasy stories. And Sanzo from Saiyuki (:
